author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
Get ready to learn about everyone's favorite pint-sized hero, Jeff the Land Shark! Dive into Jeff's short but hilarious comics' history, from hanging out with Deadpool and chasing down Shadow Jeff, to his role as a strategist hero in Marvel Games and NetEase Games Marvel Rivals. Learn why people can't get enough of the little guy with the big appetite.
